  "hints": [
    {
      "content": "We want to put the largest digit in the highest place value. \n\nWhich digit is the largest? ",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "$\\maroonD7$ is the largest digit, and we want to put it in the position with the highest place value.   \n\nSo $\\maroonD7$ will be in the hundreds place: \n $\\maroonD{7}~\\_~\\_$.",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "Now we need to do the same thing with the next largest digit:  $\\blueE4$.  \n\nSo $\\blueE4$ goes in the tens place:  \n\n$\\maroonD{7}~\\blueE4~\\_$   ",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "The smallest digit is the $\\purpleD1$.  The  $\\purpleD1$ goes in the ones place:  \n\n$\\maroonD{7}\\blueE4\\purpleD1$\n",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "The greatest possible number we can make is $\\maroonD{7}\\blueE4\\purpleD1$.",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    }
